== Cyclic shift matrix ==
In the case of formula_65, when the eigenvalues are the complex roots of unity, the companion matrix and its transpose both reduce to Sylvester&#x27;s cyclic shift matrix, a circulant matrix.

== Multiplication map on a simple field extension ==
